	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratiam et pacem a domino.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid a te fieri velint scholarchae<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Zu den Schulverordneten vgl. oben <ref target="file11417">Nr. 1374</ref>, Anm. 1.</note>, indicavit literis <persName ref="p167" cert="high">Ammianus</persName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Der Brief des Schulherrn <persName ref="p167" cert="high">Johann Jakob Ammann</persName>, durch den <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gwalther</persName> angewiesen wurde, zur Fortsetzung seines Studiums nach <placeName ref="l311" cert="high">Marburg</placeName> zu ziehen, ist nicht erhalten.</note>.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Huic tu scribes, quicquid rerum tuarum velis agi coram scholarchis.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interea non prohibeo, quo minus mihi etiam, quae velis, scribas; sed istum porro habebis apud istos patronum.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego patris curam non abiiciam, modo tu respondeas meae expectationi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">A <placeName ref="l311" cert="high">Marpurgo</placeName> celeriter studiorum et ecclesiae rationem et statum significabis: Qualis sit religio, an religio nostra traducatur publice, qui professores sint et quae studia, quis sumptus faciendus.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod si videbitur, mittemus <placeName ref="l311" cert="high">Marpurgum</placeName> <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="p3988">Wolphium</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8461" cert="high">Wickium</persName> etc<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" ana="bio" n="3">Gemeint sind <persName ref="p3988" cert="high">Johannes Wolf</persName>, <persName ref="p8461" cert="high">Hans Jakob Wick</persName> und <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Johannes Haller</persName>, die zu diesem Zeitpunkt noch in <placeName ref="l512" cert="high">Tübingen</placeName> studierten.</note>.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praeterea inhortaberis <persName ref="p8363" cert="high">Noviomagum</persName><note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4"><persName ref="p8363" cert="high">Gerhard Geldenhauer</persName>.</note>, ad illa mihi capita respondeat<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullinger</persName> hatte sich in einem nicht mehr vorhandenen Brief nach der <placeName ref="l311" cert="high">Marburger</placeName> Schule erkundigt; vgl. <persName ref="p8363" cert="high">Geldenhauers</persName> Antwort vom 30. Juni (unten <ref target="file11450">Nr. 1407</ref>).</note>.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non licuit illi copiosius scribere.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hisce enim diebus celebramus synodum<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Die Frühjahrssynode des Jahres 1540 fand am 11. Mai statt, s. Zürich StA, E II 1, 239.</note>.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Itaque factum est, ut illi brevem tantum tui commendationem scripserim<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Auch dieses zweite Schreiben ist verloren.</note>.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Agito ergo apud illum optima fide, quae tibi mando, et vide, pius sis, sedulus et probus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale, mi fili.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salvum te vult familia.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">11. maii 1540.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">H. Bullingerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Rodolpho Gvalthero</persName> <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileae</placeName> in aedibus d. <persName ref="p8418" cert="high">Myconii</persName> agenti, filio.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
